marketing: Shell Brake Fluid DOT 3 is a heavy duty brake system and hydraulic clutch fluid for systems requiring a FMVSS No 116 DOT 3, ISO 4925 Class 3, or many other equivalent specifications in a glycol (polyglycol-ether) brake fluid.
